# GhostChat

Read `AGENTS.md` at the repo root before large changes.

## Non-negotiables

- Server is ciphertext-only relay (Cloudflare Worker + Durable Objects).
- No message history storage. No private keys server-side.
- Max 2 participants per room; session identity = `sessionToken`.
- Protocol types: `packages/protocol`. Crypto: `packages/crypto`.
- Use pnpm. After package edits: `pnpm build:packages`.
- Verify with `pnpm typecheck` and `pnpm test` when possible.
- Mobile-first web UI; do not break room `app-shell` / safe-area layout.
- Prefer 127.0.0.1 for local worker WebSocket URLs.

## Key files

- `apps/worker/src/room.ts` — room lifecycle, join, relay
- `apps/web/src/hooks/useGhostRoom.ts` — client E2EE + WS
- `packages/protocol/src/index.ts` — wire format
